long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_GB,en_US,e:
Do you need to convert files online from one format to another, or even from one file category to another? We’ve got you covered!

Focus on a file category, or a specific format and follow easy to use three-step conversion process:

✅  Add files
✅  Choose the right format
✅  Download files.

Are you wondering how many file categories you can choose from using this free online converter? We didn’t just count them, we created category converters inside of converter, and here are all of them:

▶️ Archive Converter,
▶️ Audio Converter,
▶️ Documents Converter,
▶️ E-books Converter,
▶️ Images Converter,
▶️ Presentations Converter,
▶️ Spreadsheet Converter,
▶️ Video Converter.

We have the right tool for all your file dilemmas and the reliable information that will help you with your decisions, at least when it comes to those regarding file formats.

For your favorite images, besides JPG, you can use the following: CR2, 3FR, EPS, GIF, NEF, ARW, DCR, JPEG, SVG, PSD, PPM, TIF, TIFF, and CXF.
You know about PDF and DOCX files, but have you heard about these document formats CSV, DJVU, DOC, HTML, KEY, NUMBERS, ODP, ODS, ODT, PAGES, PPS, PPSX, PPT, PPTX, PS, RTF, TXT, VSD, WPD, WPS, XPS?

Music comes in different genres, but also in formats such as AAC, AC3, AIF, AIFC, AIFF, AMR, AU, CAF, FLAC, M4A, M4B, MP3, OGA, SFARK, VOC, WAV, WEBA, and WMA.

Videos are the most powerful tool for digital communication, and you are well-aware that they come in different formats too. Those are 3G2, 3GP, and 3GPP, AVI, CAVS, DV, DVR, FLV, M2TS, M4V, MKV, MOD, MOV, MP4, MPEG, MPG, MTS, MXF, OGG, RM, RMVB, SWF, TS, VOB, WEBM, WMV, and WTV.

Bibliophiles enjoy listening to their favorite chapters stored in one of the following e-book file formats: AZW, AZW3, AZW4, CBC, CBR, CBZ, CHM, EPUB, FB2, HTM, HTMLZ, LIT, LRF, MOBI, PDB, PML, PRC, RB, SNB, TCR, and TXTZ.

And all of the files can be stored in one of the many archives such as 7Z, ACE, ALZ, ARC, ARJ, BZ, BZ2, CAB, CPIO, DEB, DMG, GZ, IMG, ISO, JAR, LHA, LZ, LZMA, LZO, RAR, RPM, RZ, TAR, TAR.7Z, TAR.BZ, TAR.BZ2, TAR.GZ, TAR.LZO, TAR.XZ, TAR.Z, TBZ, TBZ2, TGZ, TZ, TZO, XZ, Z, and ZIP file extensions.
